data.text: @Golden_Pup @PublicHealthON Have you filed an FOIA request for that data? Curious..

@Golden_Pup @PublicHealthON I didn't even know they were tracking vaccine injuries here in Canada or even Ontario and sharing it publicly.

Interesting.

@CLFFA58 @Golden_Pup @PublicHealthON I'm one.
I'm coincidentally physically trashed now.
coincidence.
Nothing to do with the shot the day before,I can go get some more 🙄

@dowchar @Golden_Pup @CanadaSOS1 @PublicHealthON Well, the numbers are surely wrong. But not in a way they'd like. I know my and many other people's reports were written off as coincidental. The fact that one day I was normal and the next I looked and still do, like I have special needs while trying to eat, doesn't matter.

@Sunny24446460 @Golden_Pup @PublicHealthON Mine are unreported too. Doctor said public health would toss it anyway and she isn't allowed to exempt me from more.
Anybody seeing me eat now thinks I have special needs. Also anyone seeing me trying to climb stairs.
@Golden_Pup @CanadaSOS1 @PublicHealthON But some pro-vaxxer will debunk it somehow 🙄
@Golden_Pup @PublicHealthON healthy cousin 51, died in Jan 2 days after booster shot... heart, but not reported.
